Name: Renumbering a duplicate section number in title 19.
Title: A Local Law to amend the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to renumbering a duplicate section number in title 19.

History.Description: This Introduction was Introduced by Council
This Introduction was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on Transportation
This Introduction was Sine Die (Filed, End of Session)

Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:

	Section 1.  Subchapter 3 of chapter 1 of title 19 of the administrative code of the city of New York is amended by renumbering §19-180 entitled “Performance indicators,” as §19-183.
§2.  This local law shall take immediately.

LS # 6590
